04:33.360 --> 04:34.680
You only pay cash for stuff?

04:34.680 --> 04:41.320
Well, I'm not quite as bad a storeman, but I carry a bit of cash with me in just in case

04:41.320 --> 04:42.320
things go wrong.

04:42.320 --> 04:48.400
