06:14.120 --> 06:18.360
If it's all just contactless payments and card payments, it's just much easier.

06:18.360 --> 06:21.280
So I totally understand why they do it, but I don't know.

06:21.280 --> 06:22.280
It does.

06:22.280 --> 06:23.880
